      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in style! This car is in good condition and has been clearly well-cared for, offering a smooth and dependable ride that you're going to love. While you might notice some very light, typical signs of previous enjoyment, it remains a fantastic and reliable choice for anyone looking for quality. It's clean, runs great, and is truly ready for its next adventure!",
