    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior presents very well, though it does have some minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches from normal use. The interior is clean and smoke-free, showing only minimal wear on the upholstery. It runs and drives smoothly, offering a reliable and comfortable experience for the next owner.",
